# Software Product Variant Model
# Example: Enterprise Software Suite Configuration

# Core Platform (must be selected)
feature CorePlatform mandatory selected
    feature Authentication mandatory selected
    feature Database mandatory selected
    feature UserManagement mandatory selected

# Deployment Options (exactly one must be selected)
feature Deployment mandatory selected
    feature Cloud alternative selected
    feature OnPremise alternative
    feature Hybrid alternative

# Analytics Module (optional)
feature Analytics optional selected
    feature BasicReporting mandatory selected
    feature AdvancedDashboards optional selected
    feature RealTimeMonitoring optional

# Integration Module (optional)
feature Integration optional
    feature RestAPI mandatory
    feature GraphQL optional
    feature Webhooks optional

# Security Features (optional but recommended)
feature Security optional selected
    feature TwoFactorAuth mandatory selected
    feature SingleSignOn optional selected
    feature AuditLogging mandatory selected 